# Retail Rewards API

# Project Overview
A RESTful API to calculate customer reward points based on transaction history.

# Tech Stack
- Java 8
- Spring Boot
- H2 Database
- JPA
- Postman
- JUnit & Mockito

# Reward Logic
- 2 points for every dollar spent over $100
- 1 point for every dollar spent between $50 and $100

# API Endpoint(Postman)

# Post 
http://localhost:2318/api/rewards/customer

#Get 
Customer Id= 101
http://localhost:2318/api/rewards/calculate/101?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-03-31

customerId =201
http://localhost:2318/api/rewards/calculate/201?startDate=2025-07-01&endDate=2025-09-15

customerId=301
http://localhost:2318/api/rewards/calculate/301?startDate=2025-07-01&endDate=2025-09-15



==>Response<== :
json
//VALID REQUEST
http://localhost:2318/api/rewards/customer
{
 "customerId": "402",
 "customerName":"Hritik Bhosale",
 "amount": 111,
 "transactionDate": "2025-06-11"
}
 



//INVALID REQUEST
{
 "customerId": 401,
 "startDate": "2025-10-01",
 "endDate": "2025-09-01"
}


{
 "customerId": null,
 "startDate": null,
 "endDate": null
}
 ]
}
